                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18131027-71-off404 t18131027-71-cd405"></join>, three sheets, value 22 s. two shifts, value 8 s. and a shirt, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18131027-71-victim760" type="victimName">
